{"title":"技术革新一片红","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术革新一片红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马达唱得欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉火笑得甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼钢丢掉扒和锹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢流滚滚红浪翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轧机轰隆隆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢龙舞长空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听机器一声吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢材密密推九重。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉耸九霄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青烟银河舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装料进料联动化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平地坐观红日吐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢城战鼓催，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革新显神威，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄齐挥智慧剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报长翅满天飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——重庆钢铁公司工人\t窍门花朵处处开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上没有路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们上得去；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下没有门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们打得开；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要思想大解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窍门花朵处处开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——重庆天原化工厂工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过云雾上青天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层云雾绕山巅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轨道铺在白云间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缆车儎货云上走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过云雾上青天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——重庆港务局工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今扁担废木头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山一定要低头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水让路两边流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前扁担压人走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今扁担废木头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——重庆朝天门搬运站工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛一眨一匹墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小瓦刀呀小瓦刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这次你该休息了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搁在一边不管你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用我的新大瓢，〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛一眨一匹墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色砖墙入云霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——重庆钢铁公司工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕大瓢即瓦工铺灰先进工具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比手工操作工效高四倍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻江倒海闹革新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航标电气不用油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领袖指示记心头，〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万千海员齐上阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻江倒海闹革新；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航舶航标自动化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜通航里万程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江上鲜花朵朵开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰似红莲开不败。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——川江海员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕1958年毛主席乘江峡轮由重庆至武汉，途中，毛主席对"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船员说，航标也能搞电气化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡毛也能飞上天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡毛也能飞上天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白手兴家有何难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然赤手与空拳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样能把大事办！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜春风百草生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革新花朵开满园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——重庆中南橡胶厂工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几根竹竿闹革新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前担着黄浆粉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗流夹背湿衣衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今有了运输机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用机器不用电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仅靠几根竹管管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产提高四倍半。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——重庆相国寺街道运"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"输队工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤　梭　槽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万吨乌金槽内梭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如飞泉下陡坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船驳敞肚吞个够，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江水乐得翻金波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——重庆港务局工人"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}